				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "The slot definition class and its subclsses define the properties of a slot. These include the following: \n1. #slotName - The name of the slot (#slotName).\n2. #parent - the parent of the slot definition instance is its slot model {{gtClass:name=LcsSlotModel}}\n3. #domainClass - convenience method to get the domain class that this slot belongs to.\n4. #slotKind - the pragma that defines the slots type. Ex: accessorSlotDefinition\n\n8. Access Permission - Used to manage access to a slot - ex: Read, Write, etc.\n10. Logging - The slot can have a logger added to log changes/access to a slot.\n"
			}
